<div class="container">
    
    <p>Welcome <%= @email %> to <%= image_tag("app-icon.png", :style => 'height:1em;')%> Mentor Market!</p>

    <p>In only two easy steps you will be on your way to finding your next mentor</p>
   
        <ol>
            <li>Confirm your email account - verify your account so we can send you valuable reminders and notifications</li>
            <li>Make your user profile - give prospective mentors some very basic information about you</li>
        </ol>
        <p>It is completely up to you how much information you provide. More information provided may increase opportunities for mentoring relationships</p>

    <p>You can confirm your account email through the link below:</p>

    <p><%= link_to 'Confirm my account', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %></p>
    
    <div><%= image_tag("diversity.png", :style => 'height:1em;')%></div>
</div>